<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head lang="en">
    <title>Content</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
  <body> 
    <div class='container'>
      <br>
        <div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
          <h3><%= name %> was born!</h3>           
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-sm-12"></div>
              <%= message%>
            </div>
        </div>

            <div class='row'>
                <div class='col-sm-8'>
                    <ul>
                        <li class="list-unstyled">
                          <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Hungry</label> 
                          <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('hungry') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('hungry') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('hungry') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Health</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('health') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('health') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('health') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Energy</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('energy') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('energy') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('energy') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Thirst</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('thirst') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('thirst') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('thirst') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Mood</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('mood') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('mood') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('mood') %></div>
        </div>

                </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Dirty</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('dirty') %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('dirty') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('dirty') %></div>
        </div>
        </li>
                <li class="list-unstyled">
                    <label class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Lifes</label> 
                            <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar bg-success" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= get('lifes') * 20 %>%" aria-valuenow="<%= get('lifes') %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= get('lifes') %></div>
        </div>
        <br>
 
        </li>
          </ul>
            </div>
              <div class='col-sm-4'>
                <img src= "<%= image%>" class="img-fluid" alt="Responsive image">
              </div> 
            </div>
            <br>
            <hr>
            <div class='row'>
                  <form action="/play" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="play" value="play">Play</button>
                  </form>

                  <form action="/eat" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="eat" value="eat">Eat</button>
                  </form>

                  <form action="/drink" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="drink" value="drink">Drink</button>
                  </form>

                  <form action="/treat" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="treat" value="treat">Treat</button>
                  </form>

                  <form action="/grooming" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="groÐ¾ming" value="grooming">Groming</button>
                  </form>
                  <form action="/walking" method="get">
                     <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="walking" value="walking">Walking</button>
                  </form>

                  <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseExample" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">HELP</button>
                    <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
                      <div class="card card-body bg-light">
                        <p>If you use a 'play' action, then you will improve his <strong>health</strong>, but decreases <strong>energy</strong> and increases <strong>hungry, dirty, thirst</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'eat' action, then you will improve his <strong>health</strong>, <strong>mood</strong> but decreases <strong>energy</strong> and <strong>hungry</strong>, <strong>thirst</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'drink' action, then you will improve his <strong>health</strong> but decreases <strong>mood</strong> and <strong>thirst</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'treat' action, then you will improve <strong>all parameters</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'dream' action, then you will decreases <strong>all parameters</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'awake' action, then you will decreases  <strong>energy</strong>, <strong>mood</strong>, but increases <strong>hungry</strong>, <strong>dirty</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'overwatch' action, then a random action will be performed.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'grooming' action, then you will improve <strong>health</strong> and <strong>energy</strong>, decreases <strong>mood</strong>, <strong>hungry</strong>, <strong>dirty</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'restroom' action, then you will improve <strong>health</strong> and increases <strong>dirty</strong>, <strong>thirst</strong>.</p>
                        <p>if you use a 'walking' action, then you will improve <strong>mood</strong> and increases <strong>dirty</strong>, and decreases <strong>energy</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'hug_pet' action, then you will improve <strong>mood</strong> and <strong>health</strong>.</p>
                        <p>If you use a 'pet_status' action, then it will display the current characteristics of the pet from 0 to 100.</p>
                        <p>Also every 10 minutes the pet's characteristics will decrease during the game.</p>
                      </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ZMP7rVo3mIykV+2+9J3UJ46jBk0WLaUAdn689aCwoqbBJiSnjAK/l8WvCWPIPm49" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-ChfqqxuZUCnJSK3+MXmPNIyE6ZbWh2IMqE241rYiqJxyMiZ6OW/JmZQ5stwEULTy" crossorigin="anonymous"></script></body>
</html>
